{"tid":2028670,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大事件《MOMOLAND確定回歸 加入6月女團大戰 》MOMOLAND 屌打其他團啦","createTime":"2020-05-22T02:32:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T09:27:48.000Z","uid":171598,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b5806076ed554da6171378dfc6682a96b6a0f906","tid":2028670,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:32:36.000Z","msg":"MOMOLAND確定回歸 加入6月女團大戰<br />\n<br />\nbnt新聞<br />\n<br />\n2020年5月15日 01:56<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E0MkWSF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE0MkWSF.jpg&h=b5014ce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbnt新聞訊 韓國女子組合MOMOLAND將於6月加入女團大戰。<br />\n<br />\n15日，據媒體報道稱多位相關人士透露MOMOLAND確定於6月初回歸，已於最近完成了新曲的錄音，正在進行最後的練習。因此這是MOMOLAND繼去年12月發表「Thumbs Up」之後時隔5個月發行新曲。據悉，此次新曲在展現MOMOLAND專屬的輕快活潑特有魅力的同時，也挑戰了新的概念。<br />\n<br />\n就此，在TWICE、BLACKPINK、宇宙少女等一致宣布回歸的6月女團大戰中，MOMOLAND將會展現出怎樣的活躍備受期待。Phoebe/文 MLD ENT/圖<br />\n<br />\nbnt新聞 投稿郵箱&nbsp;news@bntnews.cn<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">我愛❤MOMOLAND<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">我愛❤Nancy<br />\n我愛❤妍雨</span></div></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A3LFcrV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA3LFcrV.gif&h=2631254a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fDjq70g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfDjq70g.jpg&h=df6c7211&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0001a2ed2e2ff9f56d6859f2886b4b13a6832956","tid":2028670,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:33:02.000Z","msg":"冇牙雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5b0de98c1b5bcacc9fd8934c4209b40b8386e5","tid":2028670,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:33:23.000Z","msg":"死守娛樂台<img src=\"/assets/face